1#include "pfilter.h"
2#include <stdio.h> /* for NULL */
3#include <blacklist.h>
4
5static struct blacklist *blstate;
6
7void
8pfilter_notify(int a, int fd)
9{
10 if (blstate == NULL)
11 blstate = blacklist_open();
12 if (blstate == NULL)
13 return;
14 (void)blacklist_r(blstate, a, fd, "smtpd");
15 if (a == 0) {
16 blacklist_close(blstate);
17 blstate = NULL;
18 }
19}
